---

<Layout
  title="Resources – Ranking Atlas"
  description="Primary-source research on paid link pricing, AI search visibility, and citation equity for B2B SaaS marketing teams."
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <Eyebrow label="Resources" />
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink leading-[1.1] mb-4">
        Industry Insights
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted leading-relaxed">
        The state of citation equity, AI search visibility, and editorial authority in 2026.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Resource card grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

      <a href="/resources/citation-equity" class="group md:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card border-2 border-brand/30 p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-brand transition-all duration-300 block flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-40 h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand/10 border border-brand/20">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand"></span>
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-semibold">Foundational</span>
          </span>
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-muted font-medium">Guide</div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">
          How Brands Get Cited By AI: The 2026 Guide To Citation Equity
        </h2>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4 text-lg">
          The definitional framework for citation equity. How ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, and Google AI Overviews choose which brands to cite, and what builds the pattern that puts you in the answer.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6">Published April 2026</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <img src="/assets/images/author/daniel-headshot.jpg" alt="Daniel Grainger" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full object-cover" width="32" height="32" />
            <span class="text-sm text-muted">Daniel Grainger</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-brand font-medium group-hover:underline">Read the guide →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/resources/generational-fraud" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card border border-[#0A0F1E]/8 p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#5D4FE0]/20 transition-all duration-300 block flex flex-col">
        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-brand font-medium mb-3">Data Study</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-4 leading-snug group-hover:text-[#5D4FE0] transition-colors">
          Americans Aged 50–64 Are the Most Fraud-Vulnerable Generation
        </h2>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
          A composite index built from six federal and survey sources ranks generational fraud risk. The age group most likely to lose their identity isn't the one you'd guess.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-6">Published March 2026</p>
        <div class="mt-auto flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
            <img src="/assets/images/author/daniel-headshot.jpg" alt="Daniel Grainger" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full object-cover" width="32" height="32" />
            <span class="text-sm text-muted">Daniel Grainger</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-brand font-medium group-hover:underline">Read the study →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="/resources/chatgpt-search-visibility" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-card border border-[#0A0F1E]/8 p-8 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#5D4FE0]/20 transition-all duration-300 block flex flex-col">
